Package de.payleven.inappsdk.errors

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CallbackError
    Error that is thrown because the execution of a background task was interrupted.
    InvalidEmailError
    Error thrown when the use case provided is not valid
    InvalidPaymentInstrumentsError
    Error thrown when payment instruments provided in a request are invalid
    InvalidUseCaseError
    Error thrown when the use case provided is not valid
    InvalidUserTokenError
    Error thrown when a user token is not provided
    MissingApiKeyError
    Error thrown when the API Key is not provided
    MissingApplicationContextError
    Error thrown when the Application Context is not provided
    MissingEmailError
    Error thrown when email not provided in the call that retrieves the user token
    MissingPaymentInstrumentsError
    Error thrown when payment instruments are not provided in a request that requires payment instruments
    NetworkError
    Error that is thrown because execution was interrupted due to unreachable network.
    ValidationError
    Error thrown when the validation fails.
